CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 10, 1954, page 21, reads: "East Side View - Persons of all walks of life attended the mass meeting."
TitMainTitle: Audience of men, women, and children, gathered for police brutality meeting in the east section on the Bethel AME Church on Webster Avenue in the Hill District
